{"tid":1059839,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[省鳩我？]灣仔男生打籃球不忿食「波餅」毆傷同學被捕","createTime":"2019-03-13T11:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T21:30:54.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0cb05836c6f569bfa25eb452a113a121f567e4d","tid":1059839,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552440784_0b9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552440784_0b9b.jpg&h=8ad718ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灣仔堅尼地道一中學，早上8時25分，警方接報指學校兩名男生，因事發生爭執，互相推撞，其中一名男生額頭受傷，送院治理，警方正了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩名同為13歲男生在校內打籃球，其中一人將籃球掟向對方，對方不忿「食波餅」發脾氣揮拳還擊，令該同學頭部受傷，警方接報到場，拘捕涉襲擊男生，並將頭傷男生送院敷治。"},{"pid":"2afb0f1597cb3f62d656d85047bfe1e8e9aac721","tid":1059839,"uid":22974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d73df6791f7b670c5261186e82e3af11222a17c6","tid":1059839,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T21:08:00.000Z","msg":"玩具撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aee40e298cc10de84367025dc061030b03a5b38","tid":1059839,"uid":17103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T21:30:54.000Z","msg":"而家中學生打下交都玩報警 。。。 以前圍毆，燒垃圾筒都無人出聲"}]}